<exercise checkit-seed="0006" checkit-slug="R1" checkit-title="Linear Correlation of Variables">
  <statement>
      <p>
          A study is done comparing windchill in a city (in F), compared to windspeed (in mph) on different days.
      </p>
      
      <p>
